To have complete evaluation of the scenarios, a summation of normalized KPIs is used as a cost function (CF) and is given by:16CF=μ1Cann_capmax(Canncap)+μ2Cann_opmax(Cannop)+μ3Eco2max(Eco2)+μ4Edmax(Ed)+μ5ELossmax(ELoss)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
