				\begin{document}$$\upmu _{5}$$\end{document} are weighting coefficients to describe the significance of each term to CF. All weighting factors were set to 1. Figure 9f shows the cost function verses scenarios. The best scenarios were scenario 385, 705 and 945. The scenario lists are shown in Table 7.

